The amazing folks at @_ottostudio were kind enough to send me this gorgeous wallpaper designed by @uzo.art who is one of my FAVORITE artists! 🙌🏾

I don’t pride myself on being very handy or crafty BUT the installation was painless. The directions guide you through the process seamlessly. Truly…if I can do it, so can you! The finished product came out wonderfully and the pattern adds much needed depth and personality to our space. I love everything about it! 

Head on over to @_ottostudio and check out the other designs @uzo.art created. They’re all breathtaking! ♥️

Happy National Coming Out Day!! 🌈🌈🌈 

I came out 15 years ago. I’ve always known who I was but it took me some time to say the words openly. Would my family still love me? Would my friends leave me? How will life look? You name it I thought it. Luckily for me, my family loved on me even harder, my friends never wavered and life is pretty great so far!! 

Whether you’ve already done it, are thinking about taking the plunge or you just aren’t there yet…it’s your journey. Take as much or as little time as you need. 

Much love to you ♥️
